WEBVTT

00:00:05.800 --> 00:00:12.200
My name is Iffy. I am 35, and I am from Manchester, the red side.

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:17.600
Born and bred in Stretford, I started working in retail banking and progressed up.

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:24.200
My passion was property. I started investing in UK property and did that for six years.

00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:30.900
I realised I loved it. If I could advise people on property, why not do it somewhere I enjoy? Dubai was a no-brainer.

00:00:30.900 --> 00:00:36.200
It is massively ambitious. Everyone wants to make money. For me, it was also a better quality of life.

00:00:36.200 --> 00:00:42.100
You cannot do anything by yourself. You have to do it with a team, and there is so much opportunity here.

00:00:42.100 --> 00:00:50.200
Coming into the office is incredible. What an atmosphere. I specialise in off-plan, and I want to grow with this company.

00:00:55.300 --> 00:01:00.000
My biggest accomplishment was my most recent deal. It started from a coffee chat.

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:07.900
The clients wanted information about Dubai. I said, let me tell you. They were the ones who said, let us do a deal.

00:01:07.900 --> 00:01:17.900
My dad came over at 20. When I told him I was joining Kamani, he was really proud. It became a full-circle moment.

00:01:17.900 --> 00:01:23.100
My hunger, work ethic and passion are going to drive me through. I should not let standards drop.

00:01:23.100 --> 00:01:31.300
If the start time is 9 o'clock, why arrive at 9? Just because you finish at 5 or 6 pm, the work does not stop.
